                                Syrorum</title> (1875), 89.</bibl>
                        <bibl>Fr.  Müller, <title rend="italic">Die Chronologie des Simeon
                                Šanqlâwâjâ</title> (1889). (long extracts of Syr. with <abbr>GT</abbr>)</bibl>
                        <bibl>Wright, <title rend="italic">Short history of Syriac
                                literature</title>, 257–8.</bibl>
                    </listBibl>
                </div>
